::DarkMouse::


"Hang on a nano."  She pressed a few buttons and a sheet of paper 
with the cordanants printed up.  She tore off the paper from the 
printer and handed it to Quickstrike.  "Here you are Commander.  Give 
this to Terrorsaur.  This will guide him to where you want him to go."
She thought for a moment. "Commander? How can we be sure this wolf 
will be loyal.  He betrayed HellBeast. What will stop him from 
betraying us?"
